metadata.description: The Ticket gives access to the Jane Goodall Institute Charity Gala Dinner during the Cannes Film Festival on May 23rd. A unique evening of Environmental Protection Thanks to the support of Prestigious VIPs guests, Hollywood and French actors close to Jane Goodall.The JGI Charity Gala Dinner highlights Baboon Research, Biodiversity conservation, and all education projects.
